In the last round of negotiations, this Wednesday in Vienna did not reach an agreement on the future status of the province.
Failure, after all.
Serbs and Kosovo Albanians concluded the sixth and final round of talks in Baden, Austria, on Wednesday morning, without being able to overcome divergent views on the future status of the separatist province.
